{"tid":2165321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足可唔可以陪下我","createTime":"2020-08-19T18:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T19:15:05.000Z","uid":342968,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b46ced3ccc0863219580879e27d715b7aa0cf83a","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:06:53.000Z","msg":"香港仲未光復 大家就停哂手腳<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月大家都忘記左抗爭<br />\n<br />\n其實好多手足已經轉左做Twitter 戰線<br />\n<br />\n對比起街頭抗爭，Twitter會唔會更加輕鬆呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">twitter國際戰線大家做左未啊？</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTg@TwitterHelpBot<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7waFJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7waFJX.png&h=b965a4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：自己都好少會做 ， 但由今日開始，各位手足可唔可以一齊做落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdabebaeac3d1aa7fd1160751cd5afbdf9d2e18","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"811c2f0bac7c871aa4b21c3c9e1b70810327b9e6","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0512167c2d1a0e4b9991017d2ab06fea8e5714e4","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"樓主九唔搭八 但係重點係Twitter <br />\n大家屌還屌 唔好忘記Twitter"},{"pid":"a1dde2440026748ea1ce4889d08ed9f11759db51","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"200萬人一齊分享"},{"pid":"b19b13fa23997c7ef2d3f88c961a93c63de1427c","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T18:09:11.000Z","msg":"手足歸位喇"},{"pid":"35062f21a14021ec69d9b9e6784549c06f7f1fa2","tid":2165321,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply